---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Campus & Facilities | Saraswati Shiksha Niketan Inter College"
	description="Explore the campus and facilities at Saraswati Shiksha Niketan Inter College, Ghaziabad — smart classrooms, science labs, library, sports, transport, medical, and security."
	pubDate={new Date('August 08 2021')}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
 <section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb"><a href="/">Home</a> / <span>Campus &amp; Facilities</span></div>
      <h1>Campus &amp; Facilities</h1>
      <p>A safe, well-equipped campus designed to support academics, sports, health, and everyday school life.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="card reveal"><div class="image-frame" style="margin-bottom:1rem;"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580582932707-520aed937b7b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Smart classroom with digital display board" loading="lazy" class=""></div><h3>Smart Classrooms</h3><p>Digital boards and curated multimedia content bring lessons to life across all sections.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal"><div class="image-frame" style="margin-bottom:1rem;"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554774853-b415df9eeb92?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Students conducting an experiment in the science lab" loading="lazy" class=""></div><h3>Science Laboratories</h3><p>Separate, well-equipped Physics, Chemistry, and Biology labs for hands-on experiments.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal"><div class="image-frame" style="margin-bottom:1rem;"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544717297-fa95b6ee9643?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Rows of computers in the computer laboratory" loading="lazy" class=""></div><h3>Computer Laboratory</h3><p>Modern systems supporting structured IT curriculum and coding fundamentals.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal"><div class="image-frame" style="margin-bottom:1rem;"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1497633762265-9d179a990aa6?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Bookshelves in the school library" loading="lazy" class=""></div><h3>School Library</h3><p>Over 12,000 titles across fiction, reference, and competitive exam preparation material.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal"><div class="image-frame" style="margin-bottom:1rem;"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1461896836934-ffe607ba8211?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="School playground used for sports activities" loading="lazy" class=""></div><h3>Sports Facilities</h3><p>A full-size playground for athletics, cricket, football, kabaddi, and annual sports meets.</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal"><div class="image-frame" style="margin-bottom:1rem;"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503676260728-1c00da094a0b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Students engaged in an art and craft activity" loading="lazy" class=""></div><h3>Activity &amp; Art Rooms</h3><p>Dedicated spaces for art, craft, music, and dance practice sessions.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container split">
      <div class="reveal image-frame"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558980664-10e7170b5df9?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="School bus used for student transportation" loading="lazy" class=""></div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Getting to School, Safely</span>
        <h2>Transportation</h2>
        <p class="lede">Our school bus network covers major routes across Vijay Nagar and neighbouring areas of Ghaziabad, with trained drivers and an attendant on every route.</p>
        <ul class="check-list mt-lg">
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> GPS-enabled buses for real-time tracking</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Trained drivers with verified background checks</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Attendant present on every route for younger students</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Fixed pick-up and drop points close to residential areas</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container split reverse-mobile">
      <div class="reveal image-frame"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1584982751601-97dcc096659c?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="School medical room facility" loading="lazy" class=""></div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Health &amp; Wellbeing</span>
        <h2>Medical Facilities</h2>
        <p class="lede">An on-campus medical room, staffed during school hours, ensures every minor health need is addressed promptly and parents are informed without delay.</p>
        <ul class="check-list mt-lg">
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> On-campus first-aid and medical room</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Annual health check-ups for all students</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Tie-up with a nearby hospital for emergencies</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="container split">
      <div class="reveal image-frame"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1557597774-9d273605dfa9?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="CCTV camera monitoring the school campus" loading="lazy" class=""></div>
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Peace of Mind for Parents</span>
        <h2>Security System</h2>
        <p class="lede">Campus safety is non-negotiable. Our security infrastructure is designed to give parents complete confidence in their child's environment.</p>
        <ul class="check-list mt-lg">
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> CCTV surveillance across classrooms and common areas</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Manned entry and exit points with visitor logging</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Biometric attendance for staff and senior students</li>
          <li><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Fire safety equipment and regular safety drills</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head center">
        <span class="eyebrow">Built for Learning</span>
        <h2>Infrastructure Overview</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-4">
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="stat-num" style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:2rem;color:var(--color-primary);">3.5 acres</div><p>Campus Area</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="stat-num" style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:2rem;color:var(--color-primary);">60+</div><p>Classrooms</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="stat-num" style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:2rem;color:var(--color-primary);">4</div><p>Science &amp; Computer Labs</p></div>
        <div class="card reveal text-center"><div class="stat-num" style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:2rem;color:var(--color-primary);">12+</div><p>Bus Routes</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
